## Third-Party Components

This project incorporates code from the following open-source projects:

### llama2.c
- Author: Andrej Karpathy
- License: MIT License
- Source: https://github.com/karpathy/llama2.c
- Components: Transformer architecture, inference logic, tokenizer

### ARM Optimized Routines
- Author: ARM Limited
- License: MIT License
- Source: https://github.com/ARM-software/optimized-routines
- Components: expf() implementation, math function optimizations

### gnu-efi
- Maintainers: GNU-EFI Development Team
- License: BSD License
- Source: https://sourceforge.net/projects/gnu-efi/
- Components: UEFI application framework, EFI headers and libraries

---

## Model Weights

The stories15M.bin model used with this software:
- Source: HuggingFace (karpathy/tinyllamas)
- License: Apache 2.0
- URL: https://huggingface.co/karpathy/tinyllamas

Users must download model weights separately via the provided setup.sh script.

